{"tid":322030,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我覺得好多事都係整定","createTime":"2017-07-14T13:56:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-14T16:42:52.000Z","uid":124514,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"69ea9a0a1c324d2b092af786e48868af96930df7","tid":322030,"uid":124514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T13:56:28.000Z","msg":"或者你地會話命運係整定係弱者先會講既野，佢地冇辦法發改變就賴命運，但係你地都唔可以否定整定呢樣野。<br />\n<br />\n成功既人當然可以好霸氣咁同人講人定勝天，因為佢地成功已成事實 ，佢地可以將自己既成功帶上好多光環，例如我投資成功係因為我眼光準，我既努力，佢地會將成功歸納去個人因素，但係老實講又咪係整定。<br />\n<br />\n舉另一個例子，就講考試阿，好多人好努力好努力溫書，都唔係個個會考得好到dse,有d人溫左好少但係溫中左出既範圍，有d人付出好多時間溫左大部份書，但係最後就係佢冇溫既出哂。<br />\n<br />\n我咁講唔係要否定努力而成功既人，只係想講除左你以為既努力，背後仲有好多整定既因素。<br />\n<br />\n揾女朋友男朋友，好多時都係出奇不已既情況認識，朋友搭朋友識，上網識等等，所有都係命運同緣。<br />\n<br />\n所以我仲等緊我個男朋友出現阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你地又點睇?<br />\n正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人生不嬲整定<br />\n負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />始終覺得自己爭取最重要"},{"pid":"3e495ed1bfd5cebd34491df0c53c158db4e4c537","tid":322030,"uid":124414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T13:58:53.000Z","msg":"命運控制左人生大部分"},{"pid":"108f3fb57741e08fa182581af3d2d4c00dddd6d1","tid":322030,"uid":15823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T14:04:53.000Z","msg":"自己爭取呢樣野都係整定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5c16e39e62d0b92a66200675f2a6d2f086a0aa2","tid":322030,"uid":124514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T14:12:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己爭取呢樣野都係1整定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都岩架，主動爭取、積極係性格，天賦性格都係一早已經定哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89347e33e203306bf61a6be25389c6162817a740","tid":322030,"uid":106850,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T15:19:34.000Z","msg":"Agger <br />\n樓主打喱篇嘢都係整定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我回覆你又係整定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n啲人成日以為可以逆天而行<br />\n其實個天一做係定左所有嘢<br />\n你以為贏左個天 <br />\n但係其實個天一早整定所有嘢"},{"pid":"09f3b8c2097e48a1e0f7c7ea5daca29b9d07ccfb","tid":322030,"uid":28092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T15:56:54.000Z","msg":"因會生果 果又係另一個因 我地追溯到最原始果個因就係宇宙誕生果一瞬間 任何野都已經注定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"388f6233b7c5f456bc308b89c3e4083161f38a06","tid":322030,"uid":97989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:42:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}